  "texts": [
    "After coding for the presence of citations, the authors examined all citations for veracity.",
    "To do so they took the following steps: First, the coders clicked the URL/DOI of the reference associated with each citation.",
    "If the link was incorrect/broken, the coders typed the name of the article into Google Scholar followed by EBSCO.",
    "If still unsuccessful in finding the article each coder searched the reference author's name(s) using Google Scholar and EBSCO.",
    "If this did not reveal the reference, the coders searched the journal listed in the reference to see if any article matching the reference title or authors existed."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}